entry.value: select a.grade,a.subject,cnt.block_id,block_name,block_latitude,block_longitude,cnt.district_id,district_name,max(cnt.students_count) as students_count,count(distinct a.school_id) as total_schools,sum( no_of_books_distributed) as no_of_books_distributed from textbook_distribution_aggregation as a join textbook_distribution_block_students_count_grade_sub_overall as cnt on a.block_id= cnt.block_id and a.grade=cnt.grade and a.subject = cnt.subject group by a.grade,a.subject, cnt.block_id,block_name,block_latitude,block_longitude,cnt.district_id,district_name
update log_summary set process_end_time = '${now():format("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss")}' where ff_uuid= '${zip_identifier}'
